ice|title=YotaPhone 2 combines an AMOLED and an e-ink display, but at a hefty price|language=en|accessdate=2015-02-14|archive-date=2021-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210402125511/https://www.extremetech.com/electronics/195281-yotaphone-2-combines-an-amoled-and-an-e-ink-display-but-at-a-hefty-price|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

